  &lt;td class=&quot;diff-deletedline&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;diffchange diffchange-inline&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- THIS SECTION NEEDS TO BE EXPANDED--&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
